column1:
Grade: B+ (Favorite Tracks: Holy Ghost; Canal St.; LPFJ2; Electric Body; 
Max B; Pharsyde; Wavybone; West Side Highway; M's; Dreams (Interlude); 
Everyday; Back Home // Least Favorite: L$D; Better Things) I really love this project. The song sound great. They are slow paced, I 
know. But I feel as though that they were what Long Live A$AP should have 
been. The features were great. Lil Wayne snapped and I DO MEAN SNAPPED!!! 
But others, like Kanye, had me worried. But overall, this was a good album.
